                     <interp inst="t18230910-292-person2552" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a constable. Riley gave charge of the prisoner, but I found nothing on him.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I saw a man rush by me, a man came up and said, I was concerned with him, but I am totally innocent.</p>
               <p>GUILTY. Aged 18.</p>
